WEBVTT

00:02.909 --> 00:04.276
Morning, everyone.

00:04.277 --> 00:05.811
Morning, sir.

00:05.812 --> 00:07.112
Hey, look.

00:07.113 --> 00:09.114
We're food stain buds.

00:09.115 --> 00:10.916
Who are you wearing?
Porridge?

00:10.917 --> 00:12.518
Um,

00:12.519 --> 00:14.653
oatmeal.

00:14.654 --> 00:15.754
Hmm.

00:15.755 --> 00:17.679
Oh, my God.

00:17.680 --> 00:18.824
He didn't even wipe it off.

00:18.825 --> 00:20.359
He's totally given up on life.

00:20.360 --> 00:21.694
It's loneliness.

00:21.695 --> 00:23.896
Ever since Kevin left
for his sabbatical in Paris,

00:23.897 --> 00:25.231
he hasn't been the same.

00:25.232 --> 00:26.765
I tried to get him
out of the house.

00:26.766 --> 00:29.235
I invited him to bar trivia,
but he turned me down,

00:29.236 --> 00:31.337
not that Trivia Newton John
needed the help.

00:31.338 --> 00:32.788
We're nationally ranked.
It's no big deal.

00:32.789 --> 00:34.173
You're right, it's not.

00:34.174 --> 00:35.708
Well, aren't you all
just a bunch

00:35.709 --> 00:37.776
of big-hearted dum-dums.

00:37.777 --> 00:39.879
You want to make him feel
less lonely?

00:39.880 --> 00:41.313
This is how you do it.

00:41.314 --> 00:43.549
- A case file?
- Yeah, dude loves work.

00:43.550 --> 00:45.351
I thought all
your cases were closed.

00:45.352 --> 00:46.886
You were bragging about it
so much last night,

00:46.887 --> 00:48.586
I couldn't hear the end
of the neighbors' fight.

00:48.587 --> 00:49.922
It ended in sex.
It always does.

00:49.923 --> 00:50.990
It didn't make me horny.

00:50.991 --> 00:53.092
It's a cold case
from my first year

00:53.093 --> 00:54.093
as a detective.

00:54.094 --> 00:55.427
Is it active again?

00:55.428 --> 00:56.862
No, but Holt doesn't
have to know that.

00:56.863 --> 00:58.230
So you're gonna lie to him?

00:58.231 --> 01:00.699
No, I'm going to make him
forget about his sadness

01:00.700 --> 01:03.068
through the power of...

01:03.069 --> 01:04.571
distraction!

01:07.440 --> 01:08.607
He's gone.

01:08.608 --> 01:12.420
